30/01/2003
SARAJEVO, Bosnia and Herzegovina (BiH) -- Stjepan Pocrnja, general secretary of the BiH Standing Committee for Military Matters, is expected to present a document titled "Defence Aims of BiH" at Thursday's (30 January) session of the Peace Implementation Council in Brussels.
SRNA news agency reported Wednesday that the draft introduces the concept of defence policy at a state level, stressing the need to intensify the pace of reforms in the military sector and integration into Euro-Atlantic structures.
(OHR Sources - 30/01/03;
SRNA, BBC - 29/01/03)
